Package com.cafean.client.analysis

Class Table1D

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.analysis.Table1D
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public abstract class Table1D
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    An interface describing a 1D table with one independent variable and 0 or more dependent variables.

    Columns are ordered: [Independent Variable] [ Dependent ] [ Dependent ]...
